16
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:39,770
What's an IT Asset?

17
00:00:39,770 --> 00:00:42,940
Well, an IT Asset is
any valuable component

18
00:00:42,940 --> 00:00:44,620
that can contribute to the delivery

19
00:00:44,620 --> 00:00:47,100
