value, I can control the cost,

28
00:01:03,100 --> 00:01:05,880
I can manage the risks, and
I can support decision-making

29
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:07,530
about future purchases.

30
00:01:07,530 --> 00:01:09,870
So, if I think about it
in my company, we've got

